Legend / Notes

Outer Orbs (EN#)

Represent external forces: enemies, friendly triads, or systemic feedback loops.

Can be aligned as enemy, ally, or neutral depending on RNG / pie spin.

Macro Nodes (MAC#)

Define long-term system energy, driving triad arcs and narrative tension.

Pie shorthand: 

Style (Pie1): B = Brawdy, G = Graceful, A = Austere, W = Wild, C = Calculated

Action (Pie2): C = Catalyst, S = Stabilizer, D = Dominant, P = Passive, F = Flux

Micro Nodes (MN#)

Spark individual quirks, interactions, and micro chaos.

Pie shorthand: 

Style (Pie1): I = Impulsive, C = Calculated, Cu = Curious, D = Defiant, Co = Coy

Action (Pie2): M = Mischief, T = Tease, Ch = Charm, R = Rash, Wd = Withdrawn

